<plot>Fast Future Generation is a documentary that chronicles Good Charlotte's ten date tour of Japan in September 2005. Director Marvin Scott Jarrett captures the bands interaction with Japanese culture. This is a true look at Good Charlotte in a cinematic manner with candid interviews, coupled with beautifully shot live performances.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?190317</url></doc>
